  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 63-17-76, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO REQUIRE AT LEAST SIX HOURS OF CONTINUING EDUCATION CONDUCTED BY THE MISSISSIPPI INDEPENDENT AUTO DEALERS ASSOCIATION WITHIN 12 MONTHS PRIOR TO RENEWAL OF A USED MOTOR VEHICLE DEALER'S LICENSE; TO REQUIRE THAT AT LEAST ONE HOUR OF CONTINUING EDUCATION BE RELATED TO TITLING AND TAGS, AND AT LEAST THREE HOURS BE ONSITE TRAINING; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
  },
